19. e5 dxe5 20. d6 Qd8 21. fxe5 Bxe5 22. Bd5 $36) 11. Bf4 (11. Nd2) 11... Qe7
12. Rb1 $5 {With ...a6 and a4 included, this move gains in strength.} h6 (12...
