g3-Benoni it often backfires quite badly!}) 16. Rc1 a5 (16... h6 17. g4 $3 $16)
17. g4 $1 $14 {The player with the white pieces was very well familiar with
the typical plans in this position.} b5 18. Bg5 f6 19. Bh4 a4 20. b3 axb3 21.
axb3 Ra3 22. e3 Nf7 23. Qc2 b4 24. f4 Qe7 25. Rcd1 Nb5 26. Qc4 Rb8 27. Rd2 Kh8
