1. c4 e6 2. g3 d5 3. Bg2 Nf6 4. Nf3 Be7 5. d4 O-O 6. Nc3 (6. O-O {is our move
order.} c6 7. Qc2 b6 (7... Nbd7 8. Nbd2 $1) 8. Rd1 Bb7 9. Nc3 Nbd7 10. b3 Ba6
11. Qd3 c5 12. Bb2 Rc8 13. Nb5 $1 $14) 6... c6 7. O-O Nbd7 8. Qd3 b6 9. b3 Ba6
10. Rd1 Rc8 11. Bb2 Bb4 $6 {This appears to be a random move. White had a big
advantage after} 12. a3 Bxc3 13. Qxc3 $16 {, due to his powerful bishop on b2.}
Qe7 ({Against the pair of bishops, Black is reluctant to open the centre.} 
13... c5 14. dxc5 bxc5 15. cxd5 exd5 16. Rxd5 $18) 14. Rac1 Rfd8 15. Qe3 Ne4
16. Nd2 Nd6 17. g4 Bb7 18. h3 Re8 19. a4 h6 20. c5 Ne4 21. Bxe4 dxe4 22. Nxe4
Rb8 23. Nd6 Red8 24. Nxb7 Rxb7 25. d5 Nxc5 26. dxc6 Rxd1+ 27. Rxd1 Rc7 28. Rc1
a5 29. b4 axb4 30. a5 Rxc6 31. axb6 f6 32. Bd4 b3 33. Rxc5 b2 34. Qb3 Rxc5 35.
Bxc5 Qxc5 36. b7 1-0

