1. g3 d5 2. Nf3 Nf6 3. Bg2 e6 4. d4 Be7 5. c4 O-O 6. Qc2 c6 7. O-O b6 8. b3
Nbd7 9. Rd1 Ba6 10. Nbd2 c5 11. e4 Rc8 12. exd5 exd5 13. Bb2 dxc4 14. bxc4 $16
(14. Nxc4 $5) 14... cxd4 (14... Re8 $2 15. d5 $16) 15. Nxd4 {We don't mind the
isolated pawn on c4 - White's active piece more than compensate for it.} Qc7
16. Nf5 Rfe8 17. Nxg7 $5 (17. Ne4 $1 $18) 17... Kxg7 18. Qf5 Bd6 19. Qg5+ Kf8
